sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as FastAPI Service
    participant Validator as Pydantic Validation
    participant Service as Service Layer
    participant Logs as Structured Logs

    Client->>API: HTTP request
    API->>Validator: Validate request body/query/path
    alt Valid request
        Validator-->>API: Typed model
        API->>Service: Execute use case
        Service-->>API: Response model
        API->>Logs: Safe request metadata
        API-->>Client: Success response
    else Invalid request
        Validator-->>API: Validation error
        API->>Logs: Safe error metadata
        API-->>Client: Generic validation response
    end
